reviews.text:
Came at seven pm with a party of 12 on a weekday for an event - and Service was a++ , food is exactly as shown in pictures... Everyone was very happy with everything that was ordered;
There is easy parking; ambience is okay; not a five cause it needs a make over .... If there is a second floor that would be ideal for the rest rooms for more dining space; the outside needs better signage.
Would return.
